high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the counter with the toaster and coffee maker on it.
Pick up the knife to the left of the toaster.
Turn to your right and walk to the cutting area to the left of the sink.
Slice the potato to the right of the tomato.
Carry the knife to the fridge which is located to the right of the microwave at the far end of the counter.
Open the fridge door and place the knife on the second rack from the top, close the door.
Turn to your left and walk to the cutting area to the left of the sink.
Pick up the center slice of the potato.
Turn to you right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the potato slice on the right side of the top rack, close the door; after cooling open the door, pick up the potato slice, close the door.
Turn to your left and walk to the far end of the counter to the green bin on the floor to the left of the counter.
Place the potato slice in the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, refrigerate it, place it in the green bin

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter with a toaster on top.
Pick up the yellow knife on the left of the toaster.
Turn around and go to the left side of the sink.
Slice the potato on the counter towards the back.
Turn right and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife in the middle shelf inside the refrigerator.
Turn left and go back to the sink on the right.
Pick up one slice of potato.
Turn right and go back to the front of the refrigerator.
Chill the slice of potato on the top shelf and take it out.
Turn around and go to the green recycling bin on the floor at the end of the counter.
Place the potato slice in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a chilled slice of potato into the recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the beginning of the counter on the left.  Turn left by the knife, toaster, and sponge.
Step forward and pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Slice the potato sitting to the left of the sink.
Holding the knife turn right and walk to the wall.  Turn left and face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the knife inside on the middle shelf .  Close the door.
Turn left and walk back to the sink.
Grab a slice of potato.
Turn right and walk to the wall.  Turn left and face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the knife inside on the top shelf to the right of the egg .  Close the door.  Open the door and pull out the slice of potato.
Take one step left and turn left toward the recycling bin.  Walk to the recycling bin
Put the potato slice in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Slice the potato, chill it, and put in the recycling bin.
